00:00:37.540 --> 00:00:40.960
advances in the last couple of years, we have been able to start

13
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:44.680
measuring some of these toxicities, specifically

14
00:00:45.180 --> 00:00:46.680
mutagenesis caused by the therapy.

15
00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:51.100
And the session today will show you three presentations on this subject.

16
00:00:52.440 --> 00:00:55.320
And the first speaker will be

