00:12:46.672 --> 00:12:48.892
Most prominent one is radiation.

221
00:12:50.552 --> 00:12:54.492
So first, we looked at the differences of mutation burdens

222
00:12:54.552 --> 00:12:57.072
in the SNs versus de novo cancers.

223
00:12:58.772 --> 00:13:02.762
So we can see that in meningioma and thyroid

224
00:13:02.792 --> 00:13:06.532
cancer, there's elevated mutation burdens compared with a de

225
00:13:06.592 --> 00:13:10.552
novo cancer. In breast cancer, at the first

