243
00:14:11.532 --> 00:14:14.592
So another thing that we noticed that

244
00:14:14.692 --> 00:14:18.592
SBS5, which is commonly recognized as a

245
00:14:18.692 --> 00:14:22.152
age-related signature, appear to have the highest

246
00:14:22.272 --> 00:14:26.212
abundance in our SNs. So we raised a kind of

247
00:14:26.252 --> 00:14:29.432
a bold hypothesis, can this be related to

248
00:14:29.472 --> 00:14:31.112
chemotherapy exposure?

249
00:14:32.892 --> 00:14:36.512
So first, we looked into the association between the

250
00:14:36.592 --> 00:14:40.232
SBS5 burden versus the exposure, and we

251
00:14:40.292 --> 00:14:43.792
found nitrogen mustard accolades appear to be

252
00:14:44.092 --> 00:14:47.732
