00:15:09.352 --> 00:15:12.612
experimentally? So we performed an in vitro drug treatment

260
00:15:13.252 --> 00:15:16.692
using MCF10A cell line, which is a breast

261
00:15:16.852 --> 00:15:20.542
cell line, and treated with

262
00:15:21.272 --> 00:15:25.052
cyclophosphamide and cisplatin as a positive

263
00:15:25.132 --> 00:15:29.072
